  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Identification of the theory of orthogonal polynomials in d -indeterminates with the theory of 3 -diagonal symmetric interacting Fock spaces on ℂd</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
